{"tid":736422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"企業家田家炳離世終年99歲","createTime":"2018-07-10T08:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T15:59:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"13a8b58fdfed0a6c3b72ffd809ff77daa824ca66","tid":736422,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1406189_1_20180710162129.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1406189_1_20180710162129.jpg&h=09e23da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n企業家田家炳上午離世，終年99歲。田家炳基金會在網站公布相關消息，表示懷念及深切哀悼，並向他的家人致深切慰問。<br />\n<br />\n基金會表示，田家炳於1982年創立基金會，致力捐辦社會公益事業，並以「中國的希望在教育」為信念，支持國家教育發展，基金會將秉承遺志，繼續作出貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406189-20180710.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406189-20180710.htm&d=yJ2kETKxjOjjyTvR2w%2FLZIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=011bffdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406189-20180710.htm&h=9f1ff399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406189-20180710.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fe18df581e35f49443b36e2403559e48a2e7a5fc","tid":736422,"uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c654f28bc9a7408cdb460f8ce87f0fbaaecfcd","tid":736422,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T15:59:00.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠 慚愧嗎？"}]}